<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>{{ web_page_title }}</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #020617;
            --accent: #00e0ff;
            --accent2: #22c55e;
            --text-main: #f9fafb;
            --text-muted: #9ca3af;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at top, #1e293b 0, #020617 45%, #000 100%);
            color: var(--text-main);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 24px;
        }

        .grid {
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            background-image:
                linear-gradient(rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.12) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.12) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 40px 40px;
            opacity: 0.35;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: -2;
        }

        .glow {
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at 10% 20%, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.28), transparent 55%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 80% 80%, rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.28), transparent 55%);
            filter: blur(3px);
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: -1;
        }

        .card {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 900px;
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.96);
            border-radius: 22px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.45);
            box-shadow:
                0 22px 60px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.95),
                0 0 0 1px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9);
            padding: 26px 26px 20px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            font-size: 11px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(45, 212, 191, 0.5);
            background: rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.2);
            color: #a5f3fc;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.12em;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .badge-dot {
            width: 9px;
            height: 9px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: var(--accent2);
            box-shadow: 0 0 16px var(--accent2);
        }

        .header {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 2fr) minmax(0, 1.3fr);
            gap: 24px;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }

        .header-text h1 {
            font-size: 2.6rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.12em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .highlight {
            color: var(--accent);
            text-shadow: 0 0 14px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.9);
        }

        .header-text h2 {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        .logo-wrapper {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .logo {
            position: relative;
            width: 210px;
            height: 210px;
            border-radius: 26px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.5);
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 0%, #1d4ed8, #020617);
            box-shadow:
                0 0 34px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.7),
                0 22px 40px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9);
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .logo-inner {
            position: relative;
            width: 70%;
            height: 70%;
            border-radius: 24px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.6);
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 10% 0%, rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.35), transparent 55%);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .logo-text {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: 0.2em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--text-main);
            text-shadow:
                0 0 10px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9),
                0 0 22px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.9);
        }

        .logo-tag {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 10px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            padding: 4px 10px;
            font-size: 11px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.88);
            border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.8);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.16em;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        .body {
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .body p {
            font-size: 0.98rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .pill-row {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }

        .pill {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            padding: 4px 11px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.65);
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.95);
        }

        .pill--accent {
            border-color: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.9);
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 18px;
            padding-top: 12px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(51, 65, 85, 0.9);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 8px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        .footer span strong {
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        @media (max-width: 800px) {
            .header {
                grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
            }
            .logo-wrapper {
                justify-content: flex-start;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .card {
                padding: 22px 18px 18px;
            }
            .header-text h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="grid"></div>
    <div class="glow"></div>

    <main class="card">
        <div class="badge">
            <span class="badge-dot"></span>
            <span>Laboratoire – {{ web_course_name }}</span>
        </div>

        <header class="header">
            <div class="header-text">
                <h1><span class="highlight">{{ web_team_name }}</span></h1>
                <h2>Plateforme de démonstration pour l’administration de serveurs Linux et d’infrastructures réseau automatisées.</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="logo-wrapper">
                <div class="logo">
                    <div class="logo-inner">
                        <div class="logo-text">YPF</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="logo-tag">Équipe YPF</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>

        <section class="body">
            <p>
                Ce serveur web fait partie d’un <strong>laboratoire pédagogique</strong> réalisé dans le cadre du cours
                <strong>« {{ web_course_name }} »</strong>. Il est déployé automatiquement à l’aide d’<strong>Ansible</strong>
                afin de reproduire un environnement proche du monde professionnel : automatisation, cohérence et rapidité de déploiement.
            </p>
            <p>
                Si vous voyez cette page, c’est que le playbook a fonctionné, le rôle <strong>web</strong> est opérationnel
                et l’équipe <strong>YPF</strong> démontre sa capacité à mettre en place et administrer des services web
                dans un contexte d’<strong>administration réseau technologique</strong>.
            </p>

            <div class="pill-row">
                <div class="pill pill--accent">Déploiement via Ansible</div>
                <div class="pill">Serveur web Apache</div>
                <div class="pill">Administration Linux</div>
                <div class="pill">Labo {{ web_team_name }}</div>
                <div class="pill">Cours : {{ web_course_name }}</div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <footer class="footer">
            <span>{{ web_lab_name }} – <strong>{{ web_org_name }}</strong>.</span>
            <span>Projet : <strong>{{ web_team_name }}</strong></span>
        </footer>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
